query: SELECT ?a WHERE { ?a hasName regex( <A> ) . ?a isGraspable true . ?a isReachableBy RECEIVER }
SELECT ?a WHERE { ?a hasName regex( <A> ) . SENDER isPointingAt ?a }
SELECT ?a WHERE { ?a hasName regex( <A> ) . ?a isGraspable true . ?a isReachable RECEIVER . ?a isVisibleBy RECEIVER }
SELECT ?a WHERE { ?a hasName regex( <A> ) . ?a isGraspable true . ?a isHeldBy SENDER }
SELECT ?a WHERE { ?a hasName regex( <A> ) . ?a isGraspable true . ?a isLiftable true }
SELECT ?a WHERE { ?a isA Object . ?a hasColor regex(<A>) }
SELECT ?a WHERE { ?a hasName regex( <B> ) . ?a hasColor regex(<A>) . ?a isGraspable true . ?a isReachableBy RECEIVER }
SELECT ?a WHERE { ?a hasName regex( <B> ) . ?a hasColor regex(<A>) . ?a isGraspable true . ?a isHeldBy SENDER . ?a isHeavy true }
SELECT ?a WHERE { ?a hasName regex( <B> ) . ?a hasColor regex(<A>) . ?a isGraspable true . ?a isHeldBy SENDER . ?a isLiftable true }
